  ALFONSO (auto): "Rahgot was an alchemist-priest -- environmental warfare four
    thousand years ago. Antoine isn't his apprentice; he's his SUCCESSOR. The
    plagues aren't Antoine's project. They're Rahgot's. Antoine is the instrument."
STRAIN 2.0 FOLDER (Alfonso free; others Magic TN 16):
  Goals: self-propagating; waterborne + airborne + RESTORATION-transmissible ("a
